Use Keepsafe for:

results.description:
Safety Photo+Video — Zero-Knowledge Private Vault

Your private photos and videos deserve absolute privacy.
Safety Photo+Video is a secure vault built with zero-knowledge encryption, meaning only you can access your data — not us, not the cloud, not anyone else.

Protect your most sensitive memories from prying eyes, accidental exposure, and unauthorized access, while enjoying seamless encrypted sync across your devices.

Why Choose Safety Photo+Video?
Have you ever handed your phone to someone and felt uneasy about your gallery?
Or worried that cloud services or apps might scan, analyze, or reuse your private photos?

With Safety Photo+Video, your media is protected by end-to-end, zero-knowledge encryption. Your encryption keys are generated and stored only on your device, ensuring that your photos and videos remain completely private — even when backed up to the cloud.

We can’t see your data. We don’t analyze it. We don’t use it for AI.

Advanced Privacy & Security:
• Biometric Protection — Unlock with Face ID or Touch ID
• Custom Passcodes — PIN, combination lock, or pattern lock
• Decoy Password — Show fake content while your real vault stays hidden
• Lock Individual Albums — Separate passcodes for extra protection
• Intruder Alert (AI-powered) — Automatically capture intruder attempts

Zero-Knowledge Encrypted Cloud Sync:
• End-to-End Encryption — Your data is encrypted before leaving your device
• Zero-Knowledge Architecture — Only you hold the decryption keys
• Private Cloud Backup — Restore your media securely across devices
• No Data Mining — Your photos are never used for AI or machine learning

Full Control of Your Media:
• Capture Inside the App — Photos and videos never touch your camera roll
• Private Local Processing — All processing stays on your device
• Organized Albums — Easily manage and categorize your media
• Secure PC Sync — Upload and download via web browser
• Bluetooth Sharing — Share securely with nearby Safety Photo+Video users

Why Safety Photo+Video Is Different?
Most apps claim privacy — we architect for it.

Safety Photo+Video is built with a zero-knowledge security model, meaning:
• Your files are encrypted before upload
• Encryption keys never leave your device
• Even our servers cannot access your content

Your private memories stay private — by design.

Whether you’re protecting personal moments, confidential files, or sensitive videos, Safety Photo+Video gives you complete ownership and peace of mind.

Take Back Control of Your Privacy.

Download Safety Photo+Video today and experience true zero-knowledge privacy for your photos and videos.
